you is to pretty much accept it. A good SK will ususally back off a sec or FD for agro management, but sounds like you guys are just funnin each other anyhow. You could try faster weapons, or heavy proc weapons, but even with Lammy, and Defiance, I cant pull agro off Kanr, or Colinree to save my life. Nor could I when I used the venom axe. The only weapon that would do it, was that Praetors blade of diablity.<br><br>Cheers,<br>Dvara <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udvara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dvara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/9/02 11:55:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=102.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I almost forgot,</span><hr size=1> Isnt the bonedaddy using a Strength of Grodan? If so your never gonna pull agro off that thing. Make him let you use it hehe<br><br>Dvara <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ujarkellraven.showPublicProfile?language=EN>JarkellRaven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 748<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/10/02 2:32:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=102.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I almost forgot,</span><hr size=1> A warrior will never take agro off an SK, ranger, paladin, rogue, wizard, mage, cleric, shaman, enchanter, or pretty much anyone else if they decide they want the agro.  Sorry, but you just can't come close.  They have to be careful to make sure you keep it.<br><br>Jarkell Ravensteel<br>Dawn Rising <p></p><i></i><